{"title":"刹住吃喝风！","authors":["易和元","英韬"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刹住吃喝风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易和元诗  英韬画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人三两个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪客一长串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒席一摆一大片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排场越大越体面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部长来视察，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记来蹲点……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天喜喝接风酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天又摆洗尘宴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是“长”都有份，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沾边就有缘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宴会厅里好热闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都道口福真不浅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名牌时鲜货，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好酒土特产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一连上了十几盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主人还说是便饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大手大脚惯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻松又随便，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒醉饭饱可想到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘中都是人民汗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增产节约好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不光是宣传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快刹住吃喝风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是不小的贡献！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}